race.comment: REVOLUTION BELLE (3) is building towards a win with placings at her last two runs, the latest effort a second over 1200m at Naracoorte when beaten half a length. Hard to beat once again. REAL VALENTIA (1) hasn't been far away recently including last time out when third over this track and trip. Drawn to stalk the leaders. Will give a great sight. ARTISSI (11) worked home well and finished second two days ago here. Peaking now and gets in well again with the claim. WADAANA (7) has a moderate winning strike-rate but performed well last time at Clare when beaten narrowly in fourth. Holds genuine claims on best figures and is worth keeping safe.
